rows.label: qst650302_msg0001
rows.name: There they are, all right.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0002
rows.name: Their numbers are formidable.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0003
rows.name:
That's a lot of Garlus in
such a tight space.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0004
rows.name: Looks toasty warm.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0005
rows.name:
Yeah...
I bet they came down here to
get away from the cold.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0006
rows.name:
Looks like this situation is a tad
more nuanced than we thought.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0007
rows.name:
Nuance schmuance, let's get rid
of them like we promised.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0008
rows.name:
Wait wait wait.
Inspiration just punch Tora in brain.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0009
rows.name: Oh?

rows.label: qst650302_msg0010
rows.name:
Goal is stop baddies from getting near
Sanctus Chain, yes?

rows.label: qst650302_msg0011
rows.name:
So instead of use soldiers, why not
use Garlus?

rows.label: qst650302_msg0012
rows.name: Masterpon has had rare good idea.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0013
rows.name:
If even Luxurian army cannot
pass Garlus, normal Drivers chance
close to 0%.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0014
rows.name: I see. Very nifty.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0015
rows.name: Sorry, but that's not gonna fly.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0016
rows.name:
What if some unusually smart Garlus
decides it wants to control Genbu, eh?

rows.label: qst650302_msg0017
rows.name:
Meh meh meh!
That situation very bad!

rows.label: qst650302_msg0018
rows.name:
There might be a lot of them, but
we gotta do what we gotta do.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0019
rows.name: Yeah.

rows.label: qst650302_msg0020
rows.name: Then let's go!
